These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-1::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, motorbike, van
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, cranberry, pepper
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, turkish, polish
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, hamster, goat
1. the person eating cranberry is the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the owner of the goat is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the van is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the chinese is the person eating pepper##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the van is the person eating pepper##1
7. the polish is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |
| Transport      | van  | tram       | motorbike   |
| Food          | pepper | cauliflower | cranberry |
| Nationality         | chinese  | polish | turkish    |
| Pet   | goat | goldfish       | hamster      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-2::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, jet-ski, boat
There are 3 different favourite colors: pink, light-blue, blue
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, italian, turkish
City: hannover, edinburgh, nizza
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
3. the person who likes pink is on the right of the italian##1
4. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
5. the person traveling to nizza is on the far left##1
6. the person traveling to nizza is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Transport          | quad-bike      | jet-ski  | boat        |
| Color         | blue | light-blue | pink |
| Nationality   | brazilian | italian | turkish       |
| City           | nizza     | edinburgh     | hannover      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-3::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, dunhill, montecristo
City: san-francisco, nizza, colone
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, satire, zombie
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, bellflower, daffodil
1. the person traveling to colone is the person who growsdaisy##1
2. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is in the middle##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
6. the montecristo-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |    3    |
| Cigar      | dunhill    | blend        | montecristo |
| City           | nizza    | colone | san-francisco    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | zombie             | satire  |
| Flower     | daffodil     | daisy                | bellflower  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: pear, pepper, tomato
House: wooden, ranch-style, farmhouse
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, airplane, ship
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, coffee, sprite
1. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person eating tomato is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the person eating pear is the person drinking sprite##1
5. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3     |
| Food          | pepper    | tomato  | pear      |
| House           | farmhouse    | wooden | ranch-style |
| Transport   | ship   | airplane  | motorbike     |
| Beverage   | lemonade | coffee    | sprite      |

