There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, mirinda
1. the person watching documentary movies is the person traveling to colone##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
3. the person traveling to hamburg is the person driving the bike##1
4. the person driving the bike is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking juice is the person driving the roller##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is the person traveling to prague##1
7. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Transport         | bike | roller     | motorbike   |
| City           | hamburg       | colone   | prague     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | documentary | superhero |
| Beverage           | mirinda      | juice         | lemonade  |

