The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, snowboarding, tennis
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
2. the person driving the bike is in the middle##1
3. the person who likes turquise is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
5. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |
| Birthday          | april | january       | september |
| Color   | turquise     | azure       | light-blue   |
| Transport           | scooter      | bike       | skateboard     |
| Sport         | sailing   | snowboarding | tennis  |

