The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, dressmaker, police-officer
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, trike, taxi
City: hamburg, miami, london
1. the person traveling to miami is on the far left##1
2. the dressmaker is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
3. the police-officer is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
5. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2        |     3      |
| Sport          | golf       | tennis         | swimming   |
| Job           | accountant | police-officer | dressmaker |
| Transport   | boat     | trike        | taxi        |
| City   | miami      | hamburg           | london        |

