.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-8::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, rowing, volleyball
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, coffee, juice
3 different pets are kept: bird, fish, rabbit
3 different games are played: scrabble, domino, canasta
1. the person playing scrabble is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is the person playing canasta##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is in the middle##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
6. the person playing scrabble is the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Sport         | rowing   | volleyball | weightlifting |
| Beverage   | mirinda | juice         | coffee       |
| Pet           | bird      | rabbit      | fish         |
| Game     | domino      | canasta         | scrabble          |

