.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-9::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, dubstep, rock
There 3 different types of food: radish, blueberry, grapes
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, fuchsia, chestnut
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, roller, ship
1. the person driving the ship is in the middle##1
2. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far right##1
3. the fan of dubstep is the person driving the roller##1
4. the person eating radish is the person who likes chestnut##1
5. the person eating grapes is on the far left##1
6. the fan of rock is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |     2      |    3     |
| Music-Genre       | dubstep            | electronic      | rock  |
| Food         | grapes | radish | blueberry |
| Color         | purple               | chestnut | fuchsia |
| Transport   | roller             | ship       | bus      |

