2. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
4. the fonseca-smoker is on the far right##1
5. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
6. the person who growslily is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
| Cigar           | blend | alhambra         | fonseca |
| Beverage   | 7up      | hot-chocolate | fanta     |
| Flower   | tulip   | lily       | daffodil     |
| Pet           | lizard    | goat         | bird        |

