3 different games are played: scrabble, snooker, billiard
1. the thai is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
2. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
3. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
4. the person playing snooker is on the left of the dutch##1
5. the dutch is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |
| Music-Genre           | ambient | gospel | reggae |
| Sport   | skateboarding        | sailing       | climbing     |
| Nationality   | french     | thai         | dutch     |
| Game     | billiard | snooker          | scrabble      |

