The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, sailing
1. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person driving the van is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person driving the van##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is the person playing canasta##1
5. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
6. the person playing go is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3     |
| Birthday         | october | may | september   |
| Game           | go     | scrabble    | canasta   |
| Transport   | car         | van    | helicopter   |
| Sport         | cricket       | sailing | badminton |

