3. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the pilot##1
4. the art-deco house is on the left of the person eating lime##1
5. the craftsman house is the paramedic##1
6. the engineer is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |
| House    | art-deco | wooden     | craftsman      |
| Food        | garlic | lime       | strawberry |
| Birthday       | april | july | october  |
