2. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
3. the alhambra-smoker is the person traveling to hannover##1
4. the person traveling to hannover is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the bike is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | almond-milk | cola       |
| Transport          | bike     | skateboard   | airplane       |
| City         | hannover  | paris   | san-francisco |
| Cigar   | alhambra   | dunhill       | bluemaster  |

