.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-19::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, april, october
The people have 3 different jobs:  journalist, lawyer, octobercher
3 different games are played: snooker, whist, bridge
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, aristoff, swisher
1. the person playing whist is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
2. the octobercher is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is the bluemaster-smoker##1
4. the person playing whist is the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the lawyer is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
6. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |
| Birthday      | april         | october     | march     |
| Job           | lawyer        | octobercher | journalist |
| Game   | whist        | bridge   | snooker    |
| Cigar         | swisher | bluemaster   | aristoff |

